\mt1 1 TIMOTI
\mt2 Khe Por Fharav Timoti Ndi Khergi Gap
\imt1 Khe fharav gan…®nga buni khare.
\ip Timoti, ana Garesia Ňčgu bak…®me fhain Ristra Ňčgu bak…®men guigira Zisas khoth…®gi guman kam ma. Ana ntigera Zisas khoth…®gi guma ma. Anan niamuuŇč Zudian mbik ma. Anan ndia, ana Grikar guma ma. Por ana ndigim, ana ana phorga ruav Fhe Bak…®me Ňčg…®p buni vhuuiŇč bun nzua rui Ňčaara mbui. Ndu FG 16.1 keg…®p gan…®v ves 3 th…®g…®ri. Timoti zumgum sios gari guman pan kav, ana Efesus sios gari guman pan kim, Por kha gava khergiap, ana ndi mbarigi.
\ip Por mba gava khergiap, ana fharav ana nzuai kameŇč khaŇč muuŇčgi. Por khaŇč nzuai, Timoti tuituigira mba guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, ana mbe Zisas khoth…®gi t…®va gan…®ri. Ana gumgi thari gan…®rim, mbe z…®v, mba guigira Zisas khoth…®gi t…®var farfa thari. Mba gumgi, mbe harigi khesharigi nd…®knd…®gi ki. Mbe kha khesharigi nd…®knd…®gi ga mbui. Mbe khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúKha nuiana bigi, nta nzerigi fhuvara. MaaŇč muuŇčgip, guma ana zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč ndir za mbui, ana kha nuianan mba thari, ana nta thav, ana muun r…®g…® thari.‚ÄĚ
\ip Kha fharigi buneŇč th…®gi buna bak…®me, kha gap ne nzuai, ne khare. Por rotu ga mbui t…®vir vhuuiŇč gan…®v, siosan Ňčaari gan…®nga ne nzuai.
\ip Por vh…®ra guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi gan…®nga guma ga nzuav vh…®ra siosan Ňčaara guma ga nzuav, khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúRam muuŇčgi khesharigi guma, ana sios gari guma gum siosan Ňčaara guma k…®rie?‚ÄĚ Kha gavar mpuur kameŇč, ana Timoti ga nzuai. Ana khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúAna Zisas Kraisan Ňčaara guman vhuuŇč k…®v, ana mba guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, ana bevbevira mben muunga t…®vi, ana nta nzuai.‚ÄĚ
\c 1
\ms1 Timoti wo mbui t…®vi, ana tuituigip nta gan…®v, ana vh…®ra mba siosan ki gumgi gu mbigi, ana vh…®ra tuituigip mbe gan…®ri.
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Kor 1.27\x*Gu Por, gu Krais Zisas farasarigi Ňčaara guma. Gu taagia nza ndi Fhe Bak…®men Ňčaara guma kav, nza guigira khoth…®gi guma, Krais Zisas, nza ana rarga ki. Mani nan farasarigim, gu manin Ňčaara guma ki.
\p 
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt FG 16.1; Ta 1.4\x*Timoti, ndu na phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gap, ndu guigira nan kama fara muuŇčgi. Gu kha gava khergiap, ndu ndi mbai. Nzan Ndia Fhe Bak…®me gum nza Bak…®me Krais Zisas, mani t…®var vhuun ndun muuŇčv, ndun korar muuŇčv, ndava m…®…®t…®gar ndun n…®…®Ňčrim, ndu k…®ri.
\s1 Nza mba guiguigi buni, nza za nta mbevarim, nta Ňčgirg…®ri.
\p 
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt Ga 1.6; Fi 2.24\x*Gu fhum Masedonian Ňčg…®r zav, gu mba kamen ndu suaŇčgi, gu ntigem mba kameŇčra taagiap ndu nzuai. Gu khueŇč vuzvugi, ndu Efesusra k…®v, ndu kama havharar Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuin mba gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuav, mbe guiguigi gumgi phorg…® suaŇčri.
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt 1 T 4.7; 2 T 2.14-16; Ta 1.14\x*Ndu mbe suaŇčrim, mbe mba fhura nz…®gi neŇčgi nzari kh…®ni gum, mbe won nz…®gi z…®ri zitav, mbe buni, neŇčgi, mbe nta thari. Mba khesharigi buni, nta fhura mbe nd…®knd…®gi Ňčgi buni ma. Nta mben kurarim, mbe Fhe Bak…®me khoth…®g…®rga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Nta vh…®ra mben kurarim, mbe Fhe Bak…®me nzan muun za mbui vuzvuk, mba vuzvuk, ana guigira bigi khoth…®gi t…®v, mbe tuituigip ana kaŇčgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara.
\v 5 \x - \xo 1:5 \xt Ro 13.8-10; Ga 5.14; 2 T 2.22\x*Fhe Bak…®me muun zav nza suaŇčgi Ňčaar, ana khaŇč muuŇčgi. Ndu guigira kha gumgi gu mbigi ga suaŇčrim, mbe guigira Zisas khothiv…®v, mbe Fhe Bak…®me n…®man guigira Ňčgar…®v k…®v, khueŇč kaŇčgirga, t…®vir vhuuiŇč gu t…®vi mbat…®gi. Mba t…®vi mbe nd…®knd…®gi khav…®rim, mbe guigira ndavir warir n…®…®nga.
\v 6 Gumgi mbari, mbe ntigem mba t…®vi thav, mbe fhura ŇčanŇčanav, fhura buni kh…®ni nzuai.
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt 1 T 6.4; 6.20; Ta 1.10\x*Mbe Moses suaŇčgi t…®vir harigi gumgi kh…®v…®rgeŇč vuzvugiap, mbe kh…®vi. Mbe mbe kh…®vav khueŇč nd…®knd…®gi, nza nzuai buni nta guigi guarara. Mbe maaŇč nzuav, mbe nduarira wari wo nzuai buni, mbe nta n…®…®Ňčge kaŇčgi fhuvara. Mbe vh…®ra, mbe nduarira wari wo nzuai buni, mbe nta kaŇčgi fhu.
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Ro 7.12; 7.16; 7.22\x*Nza khueŇč kaŇčgi, Moses suaŇčgi t…®vi, nta t…®vir vhuuiŇč ma. Guma tuituigip nta z…®n Ňčg…®rga, nta nzerarga.
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt Ga 3.19; 5.23\x*Moses suaŇčgi t…®vi, nta mbui Ňčaar khaŇč mbui fhuvara. Nta t…®vir vhuuiaŇč mbui gumgi gu mbigi t…®vi ndiv th…®gar mbai fhuvara. Nta mbui Ňčaar khare, nta Moses suaŇčgi t…®vi daav r…®…®r…®…®i gumgi gu mbigi, nta mben t…®vi ndiv th…®gar mbai. Nta vh…®ra k…®r Fhe Bak…®me segap, t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbui gumgi gu mbigi t…®vi ga nzuav, mbe nzuai t…®vi ma. Nta Fhe Bak…®men t…®vi thav, kha nuiana t…®vi z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuav ki t…®vi ma. Moses suaŇčgi t…®vi, nta khaŇč muuŇčgi. Guma won ndia gum niamuuŇč shogim, mani rimgi, nta ne suaŇčv ana suanga. Nta vh…®ra harigi guma shogim, ana rimgi guma, nta ne suaŇčv ana suanga.
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt Stt 19.4-5; 1 T 6.3; 2 T 4.3; Ta 1.9\x*Nta vh…®ra harigi gumgi gu mbigi ruarir wari ndi, nta ne nzuav mbe nzuai. Nta vh…®ra gumgi Sodoman kav muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi, mba khesharigi t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbui gumgi gu mbigi, nta mbe nzuav nzuai. Nta vh…®ra gumgi harigi gumgi k…®…®v, mbe ndi mbaim, mbe fura harigi gumgir Ňčaar gumgi ki gumgi ga nzuav nzuai. Nta vh…®ra bigi guiguigav, fhura kha vun ki guma z…® ziti gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuav, vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me suaŇčgi t…®vi panan nta kegi t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbui gumgi gu mbigi nta vh…®ra mbe nzuav nzuai.
\v 11 \x - \xo 1:11 \xt Ga 2.7; Kor 1.25; 1 Te 2.4; 1 T 6.15\x*Mba kameŇč ne guigira, ne Fhe Bak…®me na n…®…®Ňčgi kaman vhuueŇč vhen ki. Gu khar mba kameŇč bun nzuai. Gu bun nzuai kaman vhuueŇč khaŇč nzuai, Fhe Bak…®me ana vhava Ňčaara bak…®me phorga kim, ana ŇčkasŇčka, ana nduara guigira fharigi. Ana nduara ndikndiga guara n…®…®Ňčge ma.
\s1 Por Fhe Bak…®me ana kora muuŇčgi ne nzuav, anan ndikndigap ana phorga nzuai.
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 1:12 \xt FG 9.15; Ga 1.15-16\x*Nza Bak…®me Krais Zisas ana ŇčkasŇčkar na n…®…®Ňčgiap na khoth…®gi, gu ana Ňčaarar muunga tukt…®gi. Ana maaŇč muuŇčgiap, mba Ňčaarar muun zav nan farasarigi. Gu maaŇč muuŇčgiap ne nzuav anan ndikndigi.
\v 13 \x - \xo 1:13 \xt FG 3.17; 8.3; 9.4-5; 1 Ko 15.9-10; Ga 1.13\x*Gu guigira fhum, ana z…® nz…®…®v, gu panan ana kegap, gu buni mbat…®gir ana suaŇčgi. Gu ana muuŇčgi bigi, ana nta kaŇčgi. Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, gu mba tugen gu tuituigiap ana kaŇčgi fhu, gu vh…®ra ana khoth…®gi fhu. Gu maaŇč muuŇčgim, ana nan kora muuŇčgi.
\v 14 \x - \xo 1:14 \xt Ru 7.47; Ro 5.20; 1 Ko 15.10; 2 T 1.13\x*Nza Bak…®me Krais Zisas, ana guigira nan kora muuŇčgiap, na nd…®knd…®k khavgim, gu ana khoth…®gap, gu won ndavar harigi gumgi gu mbigi ga nd…®…®i.
\p 
\v 15 \x - \xo 1:15 \xt Ru 15.2; 19.10; Ro 5.8; 1 T 3.1; 4.9; 2 T 2.11; 1 Zo 3.5\x*Krais Zisas, nza t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbui gumgi gu mbigi, ana taagip nza ndir zav kha nuianan zergi. Kha kameŇč ne guigi guarara, kha gumgi zam kha kameŇč mbararagip, ne khoth…®g…®ri. Gu guigira t…®vi mbat…®gi ga muuŇčgi guma guar ma. Gu muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi, nta guigira kha gumgi mbui t…®vi mbat…®gi kambarigi. Gu fharav kha gumgi kharav, t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbui guma ma.
\v 16 Zisas Krais khueŇč vuzvugi, kha gumgi gu mbigi zam tuituigip khueŇč kaŇčgirga, ana t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbui gumgi gu mbigi, ana guigira mbarara mbe nzuai guma ma. Ana maaŇč muuŇčgiap fharav nan kora muuŇčgi. Mba gumgi gu mbigi ana na muuŇčgi t…®va gangip, mbe ana khoth…®g…®rga, ana zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki b…®…®Ňčb…®…®n mben n…®…®Ňčgirga.
\v 17 \x - \xo 1:17 \xt Dan 7.14; Zo 1.18; Ro 16.27; Hi 11.27; 1 Zo 4.12\x*Fhe Bak…®me zazera mbara muuŇčgiap kav Ňčgui vh…®rve gari guman pan ma. Ana r…®…®i ne fhuvara. Nza kha gumgi gu mbigi ana gangi fhu. Ana nduara guigira Fhe Bak…®me ma. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nza zazera ana z…® ndiv vun kuamkuarga, ana nduara fhara k…®rga. Ne guigira.
\s1 Timoti khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip, t…®vi mbat…®gi phorg…®p shog…®v, nta mbev…®v k…®ri.
\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 1:18 \xt 1 T 3.9; 6.9; 6.12; Zu 1.3\x*Nan kam Timoti, gu fhum Fhe Bak…®men kamthooŇč guma ndu muunga kameŇč suaŇčgi, gu ne ga nd…®rigi. Gu ne ga nd…®r…®gap, gu ndu muunga bigi bun ndu nzuai. Ndu mba Fhe Bak…®me kamthooŇč guma suaŇčgi kameŇč, ndu fhura ne gan…®rim, ne ndu ndava khav…®ri. Ndu khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip, mba t…®vi mbat…®gi phorg…®v shog…®p, nta mbev…®ri.
\v 19 Ndu mba ntarar muuŇčv guigira Zisas khoth…®g…®p ndu khueŇč kaŇčgiri, ndu Fhe Bak…®me n…®man big…®n thueŇč suaŇčv simt…®k k…®rga fhu. Gumgi mbari, mbe khueŇč kaŇčgi, mbe pham big…®n mueŇč muuŇčgi, mbe ne kaŇčgiap, mbe fhura Fhe Bak…®me gan…®rim, ana mbe muuŇčgi bigeŇč ndi th…®gar maaŇč thagi. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgiap kav, zumgum mbe Zisas khoth…®gi nd…®knd…®k za mbat…®giap, mbe kem vov, Ňčk…®…®ar t…®n ndav za mbat…®gi fara muuŇčgi.
\v 20 \x - \xo 1:20 \xt 1 Ko 5.5; 2 T 3.7-8; 4.14-15\x*Himeneus gu Areksander, mani vh…®ra mba t…®va muuŇčgim, gu mani ndim, Satan farve kh…®ngi. Mani tuituigip khueŇč kaŇčgir zav, mani wom buni mbat…®gir Fhe Bak…®me suanga fhu.
\c 2
\s1 Nza zam kha gumgi gu mbigi ga suaŇčv Fhe Bak…®me suaŇčrim, Ana mben kurkurarga.
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 2:1 \xt Jer 29.7; Ese 6.10; Ro 13.1; Ef 6.18; Fi 4.6\x*Ndu fharav muunga bigeŇč khare. Gu khaŇč t…®ga havhargiap ndu nzuai, ndu mba gumgi gu mbigi ga suaŇčrim, mbe Fhe Bak…®me phorg…®p suaŇčv, ana ndikndig…®v zam mba gumgi gu mbigir kurkurar saŇčv, ana phorg…® suaŇčv, ana nzaŇčri.
\v 2 Mbe vh…®ra Ňčgui vh…®rve gari gumgir pani gum Ňčgui gari gumgir panin kurkurar saŇčv ana phorg…®v suaŇčri. Nza maaŇč muuŇčgip tuituigip piigip, ndavi mb…®rav wari k…®v, Fhe Bak…®me suaŇčgi t…®vi, nza nta z…®n Ňčg…®rga.
\v 3 Mba khesharigi suambara mbuav Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuai t…®v, Fhe Bak…®me mba t…®va garim, ana ana r…®manin nzerigi. Ana taagiap nza ndi guma ma. Ana guigira mba khesharigi nzambari vuzvugi.
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt Ese 18.23; Zo 3.16-17; 17.3; 1 T 4.10; 2 T 2.25; 2 Pi 3.9\x*Ana maaŇč muunga, mba gumgi gu mbigi zam guigira ana buna vhuueŇč kaŇčgirga, ana taagip mbe ndigirga.
\v 5 \x - \xo 2:5 \xt Ro 3.29-30; Ga 3.20; Hi 8.6; 9.15; 12.24\x*Nza kaŇčgi, Fhe Bak…® bavira ki. Guma bavira, ana r…®g…®gera ki guma ma. Ana Fhe Bak…®me gum gumgi gu mbigi, ana mben r…®g…®gera ki. Mba guma, ana Krais Zisas ma.
\v 6 \x - \xo 2:6 \xt Mt 20.28; 1 Ko 1.6; Ga 1.4; Ef 1.7-9; 2 Te 1.10; Ta 1.3\x*Fhe Bak…®me sarigi tugara, Krais won tuma fekh…®ngiap, zam kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigi ga vhezgi. Nza mba t…®va gangiap, kaŇčgi, Fhe Bak…®me kha t…®var nza kh…®vigi. Ana zam kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigi ndirgeŇč vuzvugi.
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt FG 9.15; Ga 1.16; 2.7-8; Ef 3.7-8; 2 T 1.11\x*Fhe Bak…®me nan farasarigim, gu ana Ňčaara guma ki. Gu guigira khar nzuai. Gu guiguigi fhuvara. Ana mba harigi fhaiŇč Ňčgui gumgi gu mbigi, ana wo buna vhuuen mbe kh…®v…®rim, mbe Krais khoth…®g…®p, guigira buna vhuueŇč kaŇčgirga.
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 2:8 \xt Ais 1.15; Mal 1.11; Zo 4.21\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, gu khueŇč vuzvugi, kha nuianan ki Ňčgui gumgi, mbe zam wari won ntuun anan n…®…®Ňčgip, ana n…®man Ňčgaravra k…®v, ndavi shiav kaadogi t…®vi thav, hari Ňčgav, Fhe Bak…®me phorg…®v suaŇčri.
\s1 Ňäaari vhuuiŇč ga mbui t…®vi, nta guigira mbigir s…®…®Ňč ma.
\p 
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt 1 Pi 3.3-5\x*Harigi buna mueŇč khaŇč muuŇčgi. Gu khueŇč vuzvugi, guigira Zisas khoth…®gi mbigi, mbe fhura ferfera rui mbigi wari nz…®…® s…®…®n muuŇč thari. Mbe fhura ferfer…®p, s…®…®Ňč mbat…®gar warir muuŇčv mbark…®rga s…®…®n muuŇčv, wari won pani s…®…®Ňčv, Ňčk…®…®a vun ndagi shagi gu bigi shar…®v, gorar muuŇčgi bigi wari s…®…®Ňč thari.
\v 10 \x - \xo 2:10 \xt 1 T 5.10\x*KhaŇč nzuai mbigi, nza guigira Zisas khoth…®gap, ana z…®n vui. Mbe mbark…®rga Ňčaari vhuuiŇčra muunga. Mba t…®v ana guigira mben s…®…®Ňč guar ma.
\v 11 Nde mbigi, nde wari won th…®…®ri p…®ngip, wari mbevav, Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč ndiri.
\v 12 \x - \xo 2:12 \xt 1 Ko 14.34\x*Gu fhura mbigi garim, mbe gumgi garav Fhe Bak…®me bunin vhuuin mbe kh…®vav, mbe nzuai fhu. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Nde mbigi, nde fhura th…®…®ri p…®ngip, buni mbararari.
\v 13 \x - \xo 2:13 \xt Stt 2.7; 2.21-22; 1 Ko 11.8-9\x*Nde mbarara, Fhe Bak…®me fharav Adam ga muuŇčgiap, ana zumgum Iv ga muuŇčgi.
\v 14 \x - \xo 2:14 \xt Stt 3.1-6; 2 Ko 11.3\x*Adam ana guiguigi buni khoth…®gi fhuvara. Mbik, ana guiguigi buni khoth…®gap, ana t…®va mbat…®geŇč muuŇčgi.
\v 15 Mbigi, mbe muunga Ňčaar khare, mbe tari t…®rga. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčv, mbe zazera Krais khothiv…®v, wari won ntuur ana n…®…®Ňčv, ana n…®man Ňčgaravra k…®v, mbe guigira wari won ndavir harigi gumgi gu mbigi n…®…®Ňčv t…®vir vhuuin muunga, Fhe Bak…®me taagi mbe ndigirga. \f a \fr 2:15 \ft Kha vezar mbe Grikar kaman suaŇčgi kameŇč tuituigiap h…®gi fhuvara. \f*
\c 3
\s1 Sios gari gumgir pani, mbe t…®vir vhuuiŇč z…®n Ňčg…®ri.
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt FG 20.28; Ef 4.12; Fi 1.1; 1 T 1.15\x*Kha kameŇč ne guigi guarara, guma ana siosan guman pan k…®rgeŇč vuzvugi, ana Ňčaara vhuuŇč vuzvugi.
\v 2 \x - \xo 3:2 \xt 1 T 5.9; 2 T 2.24\x*\x - \xo 3:2 \xt Ta 1.6-9\x*Guma, ana sios gari guman pan ki, ana t…®vir vhuuiŇčra z…®n vui. Mba gumgi, ana muuŇčgi t…®va mbat…®ga thueŇč gan…®nga fhu. Ana vh…®ra muuŇč bavira k…®ri. Ana tuituigip perav, ana nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇčra z…®n Ňčg…®v, t…®vir vhuuiŇčra muuŇčri. Ana phenan zi gumgi, ana t…®var vhuuŇčra mben muuŇčv, tuituigira mbe gan…®ri. Ana vh…®ra tuituigira Fhe Bak…®me buna guareŇč kaŇčgip, ana mba harigi gumgi kh…®v…®rgeŇč kaŇčgi, mbe kh…®v…®ri.
\v 3 Ana pharar ŇčanŇčanin mb…®v ŇčanŇčan…® thari. Ana vh…®ra vhemkora ndav shiv harigi gumgi shog…® thari. Ana mbarara mbe suaŇčri. Ana Ňčk…®…®ara suaŇč muuŇč thari.
\v 4 Ana vh…®ra gangana vhuuŇčra won muuŇč gu tarir muuŇčv, won tari ga suaŇčrim, mbe ana piin k…®v, ana buni mbararav nta z…®n Ňčg…®ri.
\v 5 Guma, ana won muuŇč gu tari, ana gangan vhuun mbe mbui fhu, ana Fhe Bak…®men sios gangirga tukt…®gi fhu.
\v 6 Ntigera Fhe Bak…®me z…® panan ruagi guma, ana sios gari guman pan keg…®rga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Ana maaŇč muuŇčgirga, ana khueŇč nd…®knd…®g…®rga, gu guman vhuuŇč ma. Ana mba nd…®knd…®gar muuŇčv, r…®…®Ňčr…®…®nga, Fhe Bak…®me Satan ga nzuav suaŇčgi t…®vara muuŇčgip, ana suaŇčv suaŇčgirga.
\v 7 \x - \xo 3:7 \xt FG 22.12; 1 Ko 5.12; 2 Ko 8.21; 1 Te 4.12; 1 T 6.9\x*Guma, ana sios thav k…®rar ki gumgi n…®man, ana z…®n vhuuŇč ki, mba guma, ana sios gari guman pan k…®rga tukt…®gi. Ana z…®n vhuuŇč k…®rga fhu, mba gumgi buni mbat…®gir ana suanga, Satan won vhiar ana ndigirga.
\s1 Siosan Ňčaara gumgi, mbe t…®vir vhuuiŇčra z…®n Ňčg…®ri.
\p 
\v 8 Mba t…®vara siosan Ňčaara gumgi, mbe vh…®ra nd…®knd…®gar vhuun won Ňčaarir muuŇčri. Mbe th…®…®nkhum phuniaŇč g…® thari. Mbe pharar ŇčanŇčanin mb…® thari. Mbe fhura gumgir Ňčk…®…®a gu bigi Ňčg…® thari.
\v 9 Mbe khueŇč kaŇčgiri, mbe Fhe Bak…®me r…®mani n…®man, mbe big…®na mbat…®k thueŇč muuŇčgiap, nen simt…®ga ndi fhu. Mbe vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me nza kh…®vigi buna guareŇč, nza ne khoth…®gi, mbe mba buna guareŇč, mbe ne suira havhargiri.
\v 10 Nde fharav mben mp…®rav mben Ňčaara gan…®ri. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgip Ňčaara vhuuŇčra muunga, mbe siosan Ňčaar gumgi k…®rga.
\v 11 \x - \xo 3:11 \xt Ta 2.3\x*Mben muuiŇč, mbe vh…®ra nd…®knd…®gar vhuun mbe mbui t…®vir muuŇčri. Mbe fhura sh…®sh…®g…®p buna thuen harigi gumgi ga s…®v, buna thueŇč suaŇč thari. Mbe tuituigip piigip, mbe mba ndigi Ňčaari, nza mbe khoth…®gi, mbe tuituigip ntan muuŇčri.
\v 12 Siosan Ňčaara guma, ana mbiga bavira man k…®ri, ana vh…®ra won muuŇč gu tari ana tuituigira mbe gan…®ri.
\v 13 Siosan Ňčaara gumgi ki gumgi, mbe Ňčaara vhuuŇčra mbui, mbe z…®n vhuuŇč ki. Mbe vh…®ra guigira Krais Zisas khoth…®gi, ne bun suangen r…®vi fhu.
\s1 Fhe Bak…®men t…®vir vhuuin n…®…®eŇč, ne big…®na bak…® guareŇčra.
\p 
\v 14 Gu vhemkora mbar Ňčg…®p, ndu gan…®ngeŇč vuzvugi. Gu thav, kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, gu kha kameŇč khergip, ndu ndi maanga ne nzerara.
\v 15 \x - \xo 3:15 \xt Ef 2.19-22; 2 T 2.20\x*Gu maaŇč muuŇčgip vhemkora ndun han Ňčg…®g…®rga fhu, ndu kha buneŇč gangip, ndu nza Fhe Bak…®me nt…®…®ri muunga t…®vir vhuuiŇč, ndu nta kaŇčgip, nta z…®n Ňčg…®ri. Nza Fhe Bak…®me nt…®…®ri, nza zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki Fhe Bak…®men sios ma. Nza mba sios, k…®na havharage fara muuŇčgiap mba buna guareŇč phufurigi.
\v 16 \x - \xo 3:16 \xt Mk 16.19; Zo 1.14; 16.8-9; 1 Pi 1.12; 3.18\x*Nza tuituigiap khueŇč kaŇčgi, Fhe Bak…®me mbui t…®vir buna n…®…®eŇč, ne guigira big…®na bak…® guareŇč ma. Mba buneŇč, Fhe Bak…®me nen nza kh…®vigi, ne khaŇč muuŇčgi.
\b
\q1 Ana guma guarara gegim, kha gumgi gu mbigi ana gangi.
\q1 Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar khuen nza kh…®vigi, ana wo bun nzuai, ne guigi guarara.
\q1 Fhe Bak…®me enseri, mbe vh…®ra ana gangi.
\q1 Kha nuianan ki gumgi vov, ana buni vhuuiŇč bun za kha gumgi ga suaŇčgi.
\q1 Za kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigi, mbe mbari ana khoth…®gi.
\q1 Fhe Bak…®me ana ndigap, vun ndagim, ana z…® bak…®me ndigi.
\b
\c 4
\s1 Kha khesharigi guiguigi buni, nta gumgi gu mbigi nd…®knd…®gi Ňčgi.
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 4:1 \xt 2 T 3.1; 1 Pi 1.20; 2 Pi 2.1; 3.3; 1 Zo 2.18; Zu 1.18; VB 9.20; 16.14\x*Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar thugara ph…®rav, khueŇč bun nzuav khaŇč nzuai, zumgum Zisas taagi zir…®rga tuk han mbararga, gumgi thari, mbe guigira Zisas khoth…®gi t…®v, mbe ana kueg…®rga. Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, mbe wari wo khuarir bigi guiguigi ŇčiniŇčgi mbat…®gi nzuai bunin t…®g…®p, mba ŇčiniŇčgi mbat…®gi nzuai buni, mbe nta z…®n Ňčg…®rga.
\v 2 Mba bigi guiguigi gumgi, mbe mba guiguigi bunin mba gumgi gu mbigi ga suanga. Mba gumgi, mben nd…®knd…®gi guigira pham vegim, mbe wari wo mbui t…®vi mbat…®gi, mbe nta nd…®knd…®gi fhuvara.
\v 3 \x - \xo 4:3 \xt Stt 9.3; Ro 14.6; 1 Ko 8.8; 10.30-31; Kor 2.20-21; Hi 13.4\x*Mba gumgi, mbe mani gu muuiŇč warir r…®g…®rgen guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi th…®vav, mbe vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me nza ana khoth…®gav, ana buna guareŇč kaŇčgi gumgi gu mbigi, ana nza mb…®rgeŇč nzuav muuŇčgi mba, mbe ntan mb…®rganen mbe th…®vi. Mba mba nza ntan mb…®v, nta suaŇčv Fhe Bak…®me phorg…® suaŇčv ana ndikndig…®rga.
\v 4 \x - \xo 4:4 \xt Stt 1.31; FG 10.15; Ro 14.14; 14.20; 1 Ko 10.25; Ta 1.15\x*Nza kaŇčgi, Fhe Bak…®me muuŇčgi bigi, nta zam bigir vhuuiŇčra. Nza nta gan…®v, khaŇč suanga fhu, nta bigi mbat…®gi ma. Fhuvara. Nza nta suaŇčv Fhe Bak…®me phorg…®v suaŇčv ana ndikndig…®p, nta ndirga.
\v 5 Fhe Bak…®me nzuai hegi bigi, nza nta nzuav, ana phorga nzuav ana ndikndigi buni, nta mba mba gum bigi ga muuŇčgim, nta Fhe Bak…®me n…®man Ňčgarigi.
\s1 Timoti Kraisan Ňčaara guman vhuuŇč k…®ri.
\p 
\v 6 Ndu maaŇč muuŇčgip khaŇč muuŇčgi kamen guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi ga suanga, ndu guigira Krais Zisasan Ňčaara guma vhuuŇč k…®rga. Ndu maaŇč muuŇčgiap, ndu nza mbararav khoth…®gi bunin vhuuiŇč, ndu ntan ŇčkasŇčka ndigip, ndu mba ndigi nd…®knd…®gir vhuuiŇč, ndu nta z…®n vugi.
\v 7 \x - \xo 4:7 \xt 1 T 1.4; 6.20; 2 T 2.16; 2.23; Hi 5.14\x*Gumgi mbari, mbe Fhe Bak…®me nd…®knd…®gi z…®n vui fhu. Mbe nz…®gi buni nzuav, mbigi gu thari nzuai buni nzuai. Ndu guigira k…®r nta seg…®ri. Ndu tuituigira Fhe Bak…®me nzuai t…®vi kaŇčgiri.
\v 8 \x - \xo 4:8 \xt Sng 37.4; Mt 6.33; Ro 8.28; Kor 2.23; 1 T 6.6\x*Ndu kaŇčgi, nza maaŇč muuŇčgip wari wo fhavir muuŇčgirim, nta ŇčkasŇčkagir saŇčv, nza zazera wari won fhavir muuŇčrim, nta zazera mba t…®var muunga, mba t…®v thaneŇč nzan kurarga. Nza tuituigira Fhe Bak…®me t…®vi kaŇčgip, nza ntan muunga. Mba t…®vi khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip nzan kurarga. Mba t…®vi ntige nza khar ki k…®r…® t…®vir nzan kurarga. Mba t…®vi vh…®ra, zumgum nza Fhe Bak…®me han k…®rga k…®r…® t…®vir nzan kurarga.
\v 9 \x - \xo 4:9 \xt 1 T 1.15\x*Kha kameŇč ne guigi guarara, gumgi zam ne mbararav, ne khoth…®g…®ri. \f a \fr 4:9 \ft Nza kaŇčgi fhuvara, ana khaŇč suan za mbui, maaŇčgi kameŇč ne guigi guarara. Mba kameŇč ves 8 ki o, ves 10 ki. \f*
\v 10 \x - \xo 4:10 \xt Sng 36.6; 1 Ko 4.11-12; 1 T 2.3-4\x*Zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki Fhe Bak…®me, ana taagiap za kha gumgi gu mbigi ndi guma ma. Nza ana khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, ana guigira taagiap nza ndi. Nza guigira ana khoth…®gap, anan rargap ki, ana guigira t…®vir vhuuin nza mbuim, nza maaŇč muuŇčgiap zazera Ňčaara mbat…®ga mbui.
\p 
\v 11 Ndu kha bunin mba gumgi gu mbigi ga suaŇčv kaman havharar, nta z…®n Ňčg…®r saŇčv, mbe suaŇčv mbe kh…®v…®ri.
\v 12 \x - \xo 4:12 \xt 1 Ko 16.11; Ta 2.7; 2.15; 1 Pi 5.3\x*Mbe ndu garim, ndu maneŇč guman kamara ki. Mbe khuen ndu nd…®knd…®g…® thari, ndu guma kh…®n ma. Fhuvara. Ndu t…®vir vhuuiŇčra muuŇčrim, mba Fhe Bak…®me z…®n panan ruagi gumgi gu mbigi ndun t…®vi gan…®v, nta z…®n Ňčg…®ri. Ndu nzuai buni, ndu t…®vir vhuuiŇčra mbui buni suaŇčv, ruru vhuuŇčra muuŇčv, guigira wo ndavar harigi nt…®…®ri n…®…®Ňčri, guigira Zisas khoth…®g…®p, Fhe Bak…®me vuzvugi t…®vir mbe kh…®v…®v, mbe suaŇčri.
\v 13 Gu maaŇč muuŇčgip vhemkora z…®g…®rga fhu, ndu Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč ki gava gan…®v, mba bunin n…®…®Ňčge bun guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi ga suaŇčv, Fhe Bak…®me vuzvugi t…®vir mbe kh…®v…®v, mbe suaŇčri.
\v 14 \x - \xo 4:14 \xt FG 6.6; 8.17; 13.3; 19.6; 1 T 1.18; 2 T 1.6\x*Ndu mba Fhe Bak…®me fhura ndu n…®…®Ňčgi ŇčkasŇčkar Ňčaarar muungen vhukvhug…® thari. Mba tugen sios gari gumgir pani, mbe farver ndu kh…®ngiap, guma mbe Fhe Bak…®men kamthooŇč gumgi nzuai mbugum, ndun muunga t…®vir ndu suaŇčgi.
\v 15 \x - \xo 4:15 \xt 1 T 5.22\x*Ndu zazera wo mbui Ňčaari tuituigip nta gan…®ri. Ndu khaŇč t…®g…®p ŇčkasŇčkagip mba Ňčaarar muuŇčrim, nta h…®r…®…®r vhuuŇčra muuŇčri. Ndu maaŇč muuŇčrim, mba gumgi gu mbigi ndu mbui Ňčaari gan…®rim, nta guigira nzerara h…®g…®rga.
\v 16 \x - \xo 4:16 \xt FG 20.28; Ro 11.14; 1 Ko 9.22; Ze 5.20\x*Ndu wo mbui t…®vi, ndu tuituigip nta gan…®v, mba gumgi gu mbigi kh…®vav, mbe nzuai Ňčaari, ndu vh…®ra tuituigip nta gan…®ri. Ndu khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip maaŇč muunga, ndu mba Ňčgari Ňčaarar panan, Fhe Bak…®me taagip ndu ndiv, ndu buni mbararagi gumgi gu mbigi, ana vh…®ra taagip mbe ndigirga.
\c 5
\s1 Timoti kha gumgi gu mbigi gan…®rim, mbe ana ndegi, gu ndegmbori gum, ana Ňčgugi gum bivira k…®ri.
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 5:1 \xt Wkp 19.32\x*Ndu gumgi vuri ga vheg…® thari. Ndu mbarara mbe suaŇčv, mbe ndiv th…®gar maaŇčri. Ndu won ndia g…®rg…®ra mbui t…®vara mben muuŇčri. Ndu mba t…®vara gumgir Ňčkaar muuŇčri. Ndu wo phorge regi nt…®…®ri ga mbui t…®vara mben muuŇčri.
\v 2 Ndu won ndegmbori ga mbui t…®vara, ndu mba mbigi vurir muuŇčri. Ndu wo phorge regi mbigi h…®…®riŇč ga mbui t…®vara, ndu mba mbigir Ňčkaar muuŇčri. Mba t…®v, ana guigira Fhe Bak…®me n…®man Ňčgarigi.
\s1 The mba mani vh…®zgi mbigi gan…®rie?
\p 
\v 3 MaaŇč muuŇčgip, mbiga the ana mana rimgirim, ana gan…®nga guma the ki fhu, ndu t…®var vhuuŇčra ana muuŇčri.
\v 4 \x - \xo 5:4 \xt Mt 15.4; Ef 6.1-2; 1 T 2.3\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgip, mba mana rimgi mbik, ana tari gu nz…®gi ki, ndu mben kurkurav mbe suaŇčv khaŇč mbe suaŇčri. Nde fharav Fhe Bak…®me r…®mani n…®man muunga Ňčaar khare, nde won ndegi gu ndegmbori, nz…®gi gum nz…®kmbigi gan…®ri. Mbe mba t…®vara muunga, mbe fhum mbe garav, mbe nzuav Ňčgarigi Ňčaari, mbe nta Ňčkarkarga. Fhe Bak…®me guigira mba khesharigi t…®va vuzvugi.
\p 
\v 5 \x - \xo 5:5 \xt Ru 2.37; 18.1; 18.7; FG 26.7; 1 Ko 7.32\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgip, guma the rimgirga, ana muuŇč nduara k…®rga, mba mbik khaŇč muuŇčri. Ana guigira Fhe Bak…®me khoth…®g…®p, Fhe Bak…®me ana kurkurargen rargap, zazera raa gu maan Fhe Bak…®me phorg…® suaŇčv, anan nzaŇčv, k…®ri.
\v 6 MaaŇč muuŇčgip, guma the rimgirga ana muuŇč nduara k…®v, ana wo fhava vuzvuga z…®n Ňčg…®rga, mba mbik, ana vh…®ra, ana rimgi fara muuŇčgiap ki.
\v 7 MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, ndu mba gumgi gu mbigi ga suaŇčrim, mbe t…®vir vhuuiŇčra muuŇčrim, mba gumgi gu mbigi buni mbat…®gir mbe suanga fhu.
\v 8 \x - \xo 5:8 \xt Ais 58.7; Mt 18.17; Ga 6.10; Ta 1.16\x*Ndu mbarara. MaaŇč muuŇčgip, guma the ana wo phorge r…®gi v…®z…®na bavira gari fhu, ana vh…®ra won fegutari, ana mbe gari fhu, mba guma, ana guigira Zisas khoth…®gi t…®v, ana ana thav, ana guigira guma mbat…®k ma. Nde guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi, nde mba t…®va mbuav, nde mba Zisas khoth…®gi fhuv gumgi kambarav, nde guigira t…®va mbat…®ga mbui.
\p 
\v 9 Mba mani vh…®zgi mbigi, mben r…®gar, ndu kha khesharigi mbigi z…®rira khergiri. Mba mbigi mben mpari vov, 60 kambarigi, mbe vh…®ra mani bevbevira r…®…®gia kegi. \f a \fr 5:9 \ft Nza tuituigiap kaŇčgi fhuvara. Mbe thaŇč nzuav kha z…®ri khergi. Mbe bigi kaŇčgi gumgi mbari kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui. Mbe mani vh…®zgi ndir mbigi, mbe khaŇč suaŇčgi, mbe wom harigi manin r…®g…®rga fhu. Mbe Fhe Bak…®men Ňčaarara muunga. Mbe maaŇč suaŇčgim, mbe guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi, mbe z…®ri khergi. Mbe mbe z…®ri khergiap, mbe mba gu bigir mbe gari. \f*
\v 10 \x - \xo 5:10 \xt Hi 13.2\x*Mbe mani bevbevira r…®…®gia kav, mbe mbark…®rga t…®vir vhuuiŇčra muuŇčgi z…®ri ki. Gu kha khesharigi Ňčaari vhuuiaŇč nzuai, ana won tari, ana tuituigap mbe garav, harigi Ňčguir kega zi gumgi, ana mban mbe nd…®…®v, guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi, ana mben ndikndigap, wo mbevav, fhura mben Ňčaara mbik ki fara muuŇčgi. Ana vh…®ra simt…®k ki gumgi gu mbigi, ana mben kurkurav, vh…®ra harigi khesharigi Ňčaari vhuuiaŇč muuŇčgi. Ndu mba khesharigi mbigi, ndu mbe z…®rira ndigiri. \f b \fr 5:10 \ft Ndu Zon 13.1 keg…®p gan…® Ňčg…®p ves 17 th…®g…®ri. Mbe mba tugen mbui t…®vi khare. Gumgi gu mbigi thari, ndu phenan z…®g…®rga. Ndu kaŇčgi, mbe mba tuavar zim, mba tuavar vher…®n mben Ňčkari ga muuŇčgim, mbe Ňčkari nzaŇčnzaŇčgi, nde mben Ňčkari ruagiri. Mba Ňčaar ana Ňčaarar mbik gum Ňčaara guman Ňčaar ma. Zisas, ana khaŇč wo farasegi 12 th…®gi Ňčaara gumgi ga suaŇčgi. Nde mba khesharigi t…®var muuŇčv, nde za mba harigi gumgi gu mbigir Ňčaari gumgi k…®ri. Matiu 20.25-29 th…®g…®ri. \f*
\p 
\v 11 Ndu mbigir Ňčkaa mbe mani vh…®zgi, ndu mbe z…®ri ndi thari. Mbe taagip manin r…®g…®r saŇčv ndavi khav…®v, k…®r Krais ga seg…®rga.
\v 12 Mbe maaŇč mbuav, mbe wo suaŇčgi kaaveŇč, mbe nta ph…®ra sui.
\v 13 \x - \xo 5:13 \xt 2 Te 3.11\x*Mbe vh…®ra kha t…®var muunga. Mbe vhukvhuga k…®vgiap, fhura pheni bogbog…® rurga. Mbe vhukvhugi t…®vara muunga fhuvara. Mbe vh…®ra guigira kha t…®va vuzvugirga. Mbe harigi gumgi gu mbigi mbui t…®vi mbararav, mben vh…®ri gorav, mbe z…®n maaŇčv, mbe suanga. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčv, mbe suanga buni vh…®rve nzerarga fhu. Nza mba khesharigi buni suanga fhu.
\v 14 \x - \xo 5:14 \xt 1 Ko 7.9\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, gu kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui. Mani vh…®zgi mbig…®r Ňčkara ki, mbe wom harigi manin r…®gip, tari t…®v, wari wo pheni gan…®ri. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgirga, nzan pana gumgi, mbe muuŇčgi t…®va thueŇč ga suaŇčv, buna mbat…®ga thuen nza suanga fhu.
\v 15 Ndu kaŇčgi, mba mani vh…®zgi mbig…®r Ňčkaa mbari, mbe tuavar vhuuŇč thav, mbe Satan z…®n vui.
\v 16 MaaŇč muuŇčgip, mbiga the, ana Zisas khoth…®gi, ana phorge regi mbigi thari, mben mani vh…®zgi, mba mbigara mba mani vh…®zgi mbigi gan…®ri. Ana maaŇč muunga, mba siosan ki gumgi gu mbigi mbe gan…®v, mben simt…®gi ndirga fhu. Mba siosan ki gumgi gum mbigi, mbe mani vh…®zgi mbigi, mbe guigira nduarira kim, guma the mbe gari fhuv, mbe mbe gan…®nga.
\s1 Nza Ňčaar vhuuŇčra mbui sios gari gumgir pani, nza tuituigira mbe gan…®nga.
\p 
\v 17 \x - \xo 5:17 \xt 1 Ko 16.18\x*Nde Ňčaara vhuuaŇč mbui sios gari gumgir pani, nde z…® bak…®me gum vheza vhuun mben n…®…®Ňčri. Nde fharav n…®…®nga nt…®…®ri khare, mba Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuav Ňčaara mbat…®ga mbuav, ntan gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuav, Fhe Bak…®me vuzvugi t…®vir mbe kh…®vi gumgir pani, nde fharav mben n…®…®Ňčri.
\v 18 \x - \xo 5:18 \xt Lo 25.4; Mt 10.10; Ru 10.7; 1 Ko 9.9\x*Nza kaŇčgi, Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč ki gap khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNde borombaga rezi gu bigi gurim, nde mban ana th…®v…® thari.‚ÄĚ Nza kaŇčgi, ‚ÄúŇäaara guma, ana won vheza ndir zav ana Ňčgari.‚ÄĚ
\v 19 \x - \xo 5:19 \xt Lo 17.6; 19.15; 2 Ko 13.1\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgip, guma the khaŇč suanga, ‚ÄúKha sios gari guman pan, ana big…®n mbat…®k mueŇč muuŇčgi,‚ÄĚ ndu khuarar mba bunen r…®g…® thari. Ndu mbararari, guma phuni o, phuni khegene mba buneŇč suaŇčrim, ndu ne mbararari.
\v 20 \x - \xo 5:20 \xt Lo 13.11; Ga 2.11; 2.14; Ef 5.11; Ta 1.13\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgip, sios gari guman pana the t…®va mbat…®ga thueŇč muuŇčgirim, ndu sios n…®man ana phorg…®p suaŇčv, mba bigeŇč ndiv th…®gar maaŇčri. Ndu maaŇč muuŇčgirga, mba sios gari gumgir pani, mbe rivgirga.
\s1 Timoti wo mbui t…®vi, ana tuituigip nta gan…®ri.
\p 
\v 21 \x - \xo 5:21 \xt 1 T 6.13; 2 T 2.14; 4.1\x*Gu Fhe Bak…®me gum, Krais Zisas, Fhe Bak…®men enseri ki, gu mben r…®mgi n…®man, gu khaŇč ndu nzuai. Gu ndu suaŇčgi Ňčaari, ndu tuituigira nta gan…®v, ndu mba mbui t…®va bavira za mba gumgir muuŇčri. Ndu t…®vir vhuuin gumgi ruura muuŇčv, won k…®vntogira muuŇč thari.
\v 22 \x - \xo 5:22 \xt FG 6.6; 13.3; 1 T 4.14; 2 Zo 1.11\x*Ndu Fhe Bak…®me Ňčaarar muun saŇčv fhumra farver guma the kh…®ngip, ana suaŇčv Fhe Bak…®me phorg…®v suaŇč thari. Ndu muuŇčv k…®v, harigi gumgi t…®vi mbat…®gi nduiga ndave r…®g…®rga. Ndu tuituigip wo gan…®v, ndu Fhe Bak…®me n…®man Ňčgaravra k…®ri.
\p 
\v 23 Ndu mb…® kh…®nara pi t…®v, ndu ana thari. Ndu tugi tharir wain bisanera mb…®ri, ndu wo ndava vhen ki r…®mr…®ma suaŇčv, mba r…®mr…®m ndu ndava vhen kav, zazera ndun hi.
\p 
\v 24 Gumgi mbari, nza mbe mbui t…®vi mbat…®gi, nza nta kaŇčgi. Mben t…®vi mbat…®gi, mbe rarga mbur ki. Mbe zumgum mba t…®vi mbat…®gi, mbe suaŇčv suaŇčgirga. Gumgi mbari, mben t…®vi mbat…®gi, nza nta kaŇčgi fhu, nta zorgap ki. Nta zumgum k…®rar h…®rga.
\v 25 Mba t…®vara, t…®vir vhuuiŇč mbari k…®rar hi, nza nta gari. T…®vir vhuuiŇč mbari, nta vhemkora k…®rar hi fhuvara. Nta mbara muuŇčgip zorg…® keg…®rga fhuvara.
\c 6
\s1 Fhura Ňčaara kh…®na mbui Ňčaara gumgi, mbe t…®vir vhuuiŇčra muuŇčri.
