\v 1 \x - \xo 6:1 \xt Ro 2.24; Ef 6.5; Kor 3.22; Ta 2.5; 2.8-9; 1 Pi 2.18\x*Guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi, mbe fhura harigi gumgir Ňčaara gumgi kh…®ni k…®ri, mbe vh…®ra wari gari gumgir pani, mbe mben piin k…®v, mbe z…®ri ndiv vun kuamkuari. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčrim, mbe gari gumgir pani, mbe buni mbat…®gir Fhe Bak…®me z…® suanga fhu. Mbe vh…®ra buni mbat…®gir nza guigira Zisas khoth…®gi t…®v, mbe ana suanga fhu.
