\v 2 \x - \xo 6:2 \xt Kor 4.1; 1 T 4.11; Fm 1.16\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgip, Ňčaara guma kh…®na the gari guman pan, ana guigira Zisas khoth…®gi guma ma. Ana Ňčaara guma kha nd…®knd…®gar ana muuŇč thari, ‚ÄúAna, Ňčka guigira Zisas khoth…®gi fek gu Ňčguk ma.‚ÄĚ Ana mba nd…®knd…®gar muuŇčgip, ana buni daaŇč su thari. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Ana kha nd…®knd…®gar ana muuŇčri, ‚ÄúGu kha kurkurav Ňčgari guma, ana guigira Zisas khoth…®gi guma ma. Gu maaŇč muuŇčgiap guigira ndavar ana n…®…®Ňčgi.‚ÄĚ Ana mba nd…®knd…®gar muunga, mba nd…®knd…®k, ana khav…®rga, ana Ňčaara vhuun muunga. Ndu zazera t…®vir vhuuin muun saŇčv, mba gumgi gu mbigi ga suaŇčv mbe kh…®v…®v, ndu gu suaŇčgi t…®var muun saŇčv, mben nd…®knd…®gi khav…®ri.
\s1 Guigira Ňčk…®…®a vuzvugi t…®v, ana za kha t…®vi mbat…®gir n…®…®Ňčge ma.
\p 
\v 3-4 \x - \xo 6:3-4 \xt Ga 1.6-9; 2 T 1.13\x*\x - \xo 6:3-4 \xt 1 Ko 8.2; 1 T 1.4; 1.7; 2 T 2.23; Ta 3.9\x*Nza Bak…®me Zisas Krais bunin vhuuiŇč, nta tuituigiap Fhe Bak…®men t…®vir vhuuin nza kh…®vav, nza nzuai. MaaŇč muuŇčgip, guma the mba buni vhuuiŇč thav, ana harigi khesharigi bunin gumgi kh…®vi, mba buni Zisas bunin vhuuiŇč fara muuŇčgi fhu, nza kaŇčgi, mba guma, ana won t…®vira vuzvugiap, ana fhura r…®…®r…®…®i. Ana big…®n thueŇč kaŇčgi fhu. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Ana bigi kaadogap, hurar bigi ga mbuav, kambai nd…®knd…®gi ga mbuav bigi bisarire ga nzuav, fhura daai. Kha khesharigi buni, nta gumgi ga mbuim, mbe harigi gumgi ga nzuav ndavi shi. Mbe ndavi shiav, wari daav, wari nz…®…®av, nd…®knd…®gi mbat…®gir harigi gumgi ga mbui.
\v 5 \x - \xo 6:5 \xt 1 Ko 11.16; 2 T 3.8; 4.4; Ta 1.11; 1.14; 2 Pi 2.3\x*Mbe maaŇč mbuav, zazera tamtam wari ga vhegi. Mba khesharigi nd…®knd…®gi ga mbui gumgi, mben nd…®knd…®gi za ŇčanŇčangim, mbe thaneŇč buna guareŇč kaŇčgi fhu. Mbe khueŇč nd…®knd…®gi, Fhe Bak…®me z…®n vui tuav, mbe fhura Ňčk…®…®a gu bigi ndi. Zak…®ra fhuvara!
\p 
\v 6 \x - \xo 6:6 \xt Sng 37.16; Snd 15.16; Fi 4.11-12; 1 T 4.8; Hi 13.5\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgip, nza guigira Fhe Bak…®men t…®vi z…®n vuim, ana nza n…®…®Ňčgi bigi, nta tug…®ra. Nza nta nzuav Fhe Bak…®men ndikndigi. Nta mba bigi vhuuiŇč vh…®rve kambarigi.
\v 7 \x - \xo 6:7 \xt Jop 1.21; Sng 49.17; Snd 27.24; Sav 5.15\x*Nza khueŇč kaŇčgiri, nzan ndegmbori nza tegim, nza kha nuianan hegi, nza bigi thari ndiga zegi fhuvara. Nza vh…®ra kha nuiana thav taagi Ňčg…®rga, nza bigi thari ndig…® Ňčgeg…®rga fhu.
\v 8 \x - \xo 6:8 \xt Snd 30.8; Hi 13.5\x*Nza maaŇč muuŇčgip mba gum shagi k…®rga, nza khaŇč suanga, ‚ÄúKha bigi, nta tug…®rat…®gi.‚ÄĚ
\v 9 \x - \xo 6:9 \xt Snd 23.4; 28.22; Mt 13.22; 1 T 1.19; 3.7; Ze 5.1\x*Guma Ňčk…®…®a vh…®rve gum bigi vh…®rve vuzvugi, mba guma mparmpare anan h…®g…®p, vhia farar muuŇčgip anan suirarga. Mba vuzvuk bigi mbat…®gi vh…®rver muun saŇčv mben ndavi khav…®rga. Mba vuzvuk mben farfagirim, mbe guigira ŇčanŇčangirga. Mbe mba t…®var muuŇčv za mbat…®girga.
\v 10 \x - \xo 6:10 \xt Kis 23.8; Lo 16.19; Ef 5.5\x*Guigira Ňčk…®…®a vuzvugap, nta nzuav thagine mbui t…®v, ana mbark…®rga t…®vi mbat…®gir n…®…®Ňčge ma. Gumgi mbari, mbe guigira Ňčk…®…®a vuzvugi. Mba t…®v, mbe Ňčg…®rgim, mbe guigira Zisas khothiv…® thav, mbe simt…®gi baik…®vi wari ga nd…®…®i. \fig Gumgi mbari guigira Ňčk…®…®a vuzvugi. (6.10)|src="LB00173C.tif" size="col" copy="Horace Knowles/Louise Bass" ref="6.10"\fig*
\s1 Nza kh…®r…®v khuafuv, nza zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč ndig…®rga.
\p 
\v 11 \x - \xo 6:11 \xt 2 T 2.22\x*Mbe maaŇč muunga, ndu, ndu Fhe Bak…®me guma ma, ndu mba khesharigi t…®vi mbat…®gi, ndu za k…®r nta seg…®p, za nta Ňčk…®…®ari. Ndu nta Ňčk…®…®av, ndu khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip, Fhe Bak…®me suaŇčv, t…®va guara z…®n Ňčg…®p, Ňčgar…®ri. Ndu nta ndiv, ndu guigira Zisas khoth…®gi t…®va guar gum guigira ndavar harigi nt…®…®ri ga nd…®…®i t…®v, ndu ana ndiv, ndu vh…®ra th…®ga havhargiap, simt…®gi ndi t…®v, ndu ana ndiv, ndu vh…®ra mbarara gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuai t…®va ndig…®ri.
\v 12 \x - \xo 6:12 \xt 1 Ko 9.25-26; 1 T 1.18; 2 T 4.7\x*Ndu guma guigira Krais khoth…®gi, ndu guigira khaŇč t…®g…®p Ňčaara mbat…®gar muuŇčv, ana nzuai t…®vi, ndu guigira nta z…®n Ňčg…®ri. MaaŇč muuŇčgip, ndu zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč ndigirga. Ndu th…®ga havhargiap, gumgi gu mbigir vh…®rve n…®man, ndu Zisas khoth…®gi ne bun nzuai, Fhe Bak…®me mba b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč ndir zav ndun kamgi.
