\v 13 \x - \xo 6:13 \xt Zo 5.21; 18.36-37; 19.11; 1 T 5.21; VB 1.5\x*Ndu b…®…®Ňčb…®…®n za kha bigi ga n…®…®Ňčgi Fhe Bak…®me gum, ndu Krais Zisas ŇčkasŇčkagiap, Pontius Pairat n…®man t…®gap, Fhe Bak…®me khoth…®gi ne bun suaŇčgi. Ndu mani r…®mani n…®man, gu kama havharar khaŇč ndu nzuai.
\v 14 \x - \xo 6:14 \xt Fi 1.6; 1.10; 1 Te 3.13; 5.23\x*Ndu mba ndigi buni, ndu tuituigira nta z…®n Ňčg…®ri. Ndu big…®n thueŇč muuŇčgirim, mba gumgi buni mbat…®gir mba bigeŇč ga suaŇč thari. Ndu tuituigira mba buni z…®n Ňčg…®v k…®rim, nza Bak…®me Zisas Krais za k…®rar h…®g…®ri.
\v 15 \x - \xo 6:15 \xt Lo 10.17; 1 T 1.11; 1.17; VB 17.14; 19.16\x*Ana Fhe Bak…®me sarigi tugara, ana h…®g…®rga. Fhe Bak…®me, ana guigira ndikndiga guara n…®…®Ňčge ma. Ana nduara za kha bigi gari. Ana za kha Ňčgui vh…®rve gari gumgir pani gari guman pan ma. Ana vh…®ra za kha gumgi bak…®vi gari Guma Bak…®me ma.
\v 16 \x - \xo 6:16 \xt Kis 33.20; Zo 6.46; Fi 4.20; Zu 1.25\x*Ana nduara r…®…®i ne fhuvara. Ana vhava Ňčaara bak…®me ki, nza ana han Ňčg…®g…®rga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Guma the, ana gangi fhu, guma the, vh…®ra ana gang…®rga tukt…®gi fhuvara. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nza zazera z…® bak…®men ana n…®…®nga, ana zazera mbara muuŇčgi ŇčkasŇčka ki. Ne guigi guarara.
\s1 Ňäk…®…®a gu bigi vh…®rk…®vgi gumgi, mbe Fhe Bak…®me khoth…®g…®p, mbe harigi gumgi gu mbigir kurkurari.
